c=\"https://na.cx/i/UH5T8SZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUH5T8SZ.jpg&h=a168ec2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊包到咁仲食煙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cfd4bb95211b0ce49c2fce1155ab6be8a07876","tid":1841520,"uid":251945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"河南人整左roadblock <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYOOdms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYOOdms.jpg&h=b34171bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZzNtUO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZzNtUO.jpg&h=39793f00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4W2jj1u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4W2jj1u.jpg&h=c26bf7a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ujaH2eQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FujaH2eQ.jpg&h=33dc68f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vnr0OUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnr0OUQ.jpg&h=50811d26&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e4eqfzR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe4eqfzR.jpg&h=bb2a8dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyHWneS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyHWneS.jpg&h=cea37bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q5LMKtc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5LMKtc.jpg&h=854cdf98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFWzTmy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFWzTmy.jpg&h=c514db13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YM3eTmz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYM3eTmz.jpg&h=443562c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"173d50719e3de6a05e23b3ba690140dac49d42ce","tid":1841520,"uid":259010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"武漢市防疫指揮部23日決定參照SARS期間7天建成的「小湯山醫院」，在6天內興建一所武漢肺炎的專門醫院，定名為「火神山醫院」。不過，似乎是考量到「火神山」的床位有限，武漢市防疫指揮部25日下午決定，要在2月5日前在「火神山」旁再建一所「雷神山醫院」。<br />\n<br />\n「火神山醫院」的承建單位中建三局人員透露，火神山醫院的面積為2.5萬平方公尺，可容納1000張床，規劃在6天內建成，也就是說會在2月1日完工，2月3日投入使用。<br />\n▼挖土機通宵趕工，為了達成6天蓋出醫院的目標。（圖／新華網）<br />\n<br />\n▲▼ ▲▼武漢肺炎,武漢6天蓋出醫院,6天醫院,武漢版「小湯山醫院」定名火神山醫院。（圖／新華網）<br />\n<br />\n為了達成6天完工的目標，中建三局23日晚上就展開動作，調集上百台挖土機、推土機等施工機械抵達工地，通宵進行場平、回填等施工。主體的施工則從25日開始，整個施工期間，項目部將按照兩班倒的方式日夜不停施工，高峰期將有1500名建設者和280台套施工機械設備同時奮戰。<br />\n<br />\n不過，似乎是考量到「火神山醫院」的1000個床位不夠用，武漢市防疫指揮部25日下午3點半舉行調度會，決定在「火神山醫院」旁邊，在2月5日前再建成一所「雷神山醫院」，新增床位1300張。"},{"pid":"c296bc58a515c66b0b7545a244024f841e0009f7","tid":1841520,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f1d25c61401c64ed96ff01af513205eabf8c7ab","tid":1841520,"uid":76776,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:50:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:37:37.000Z","msg":"一毛心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9759699e09433ced88b9ccd2cc668ed57afa5e20","tid":1841520,"uid":122940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:38:26.000Z","msg":"豫獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82f3cef2eb243de20ac58a7a69fe414fcea24f7","tid":1841520,"uid":219244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e323b175e80fd9712c2a056cd0ba5e4222b66422","tid":1841520,"uid":158613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"唔科學！太政治！差！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:45:57.000Z","msg":"佢好明顯唔係比緊科學建議<br />\n<br />\n如果係純粹科學建議，佢應該考慮<br />\n1）封關嘅傳染風險 (好明顯係減低爆發風險)<br />\n2）唔封關嘅傳染風險 (好明顯係增加爆發風險)<br />\n而唔係去考慮過操作性，同埋封關嘅成本<br />\n至於點樣操作封關就係政府要諗嘅嘢喎，呢方面係政治、行政考慮唔係科學考慮[/size=6]<br />\n就好似專家組俾咗武漢市封城建議一樣，點樣執行係武漢政府嘅事，但封城風險低過唔封城就係一個科學建議，政府唔該唔好攞科學做擋箭牌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">亦都唔好將個波拋番去世衛度！<br />\n世衛決策嘅時候有冇睇埋武漢流出嘅片段？ 正常人都睇得出直情係嚴重過官方數字好多，世衛嘅決策係基於官方數據作出嘅話咁點解香港要跟住錯<br />\n</span></span><br />\n更何況乜嘢叫做前所未有？(呢個唔係科學建議啦，科學點會考慮係咪前所未有)<br />\n大陸封鎖湖北省都係前所未有，世衛一樣讚佢，香港封關可能世衛都會讚香港有效避免社區爆發"},{"pid":"3ad59935992796f075eaebf0bdf41dca8377db85","tid":1841520,"uid":193744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"相比之下，香港被特首變到窮鄉僻壤都比唔上"},{"pid":"4cee8dbbe4d2a0e24b74ee5f45766ec73f81a5ac","tid":1841520,"uid":280886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qE2y8jG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqE2y8jG.jpg&h=6e3002bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入境 海關 航空業</span><br />\n罷工救港，癱瘓關口<br />\n從源頭直接封關！<br />\n<br />\n贊同麻煩幫推幫share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c438ee5a85bdf8818357fcf88472b28a0497cfc7","tid":1841520,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1515406143bf6e28e2844c9d34bf20aeddc924eb","tid":1841520,"uid":201110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f1d25c61401c64ed96ff01af513205eabf8c7ab","tid":1841520,"uid":76776,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:50:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:10:22.000Z","msg":"Ching 點解近排講啲嘢唔同晒嘅？係咪維穩費冇再出定係你都中左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370a31a90785511262d723467aa3976ffd235f87","tid":1841520,"uid":281900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"湖南正式同武漢割蓆 從此武漢係中國獨立 史稱武漢之亂"},{"pid":"0ab2f6f6651d1531f9b873f02f82f713894c28d4","tid":1841520,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020